title: Vestal girl's soccer remains unbeaten
text:
Vestal girl's soccer remains unbeaten 
By wbng sports October 2, 2015 Updated Oct 2, 2015 at 12:49 AM EDT 
Binghamton, NY (WBNG Binghamton) Vestal remained unbeaten and unscored upon on Thursday night as the Golden Bears beat Binghamton, 7-0, in girl's soccer. 
Vestal is now 9-0 on the season and has not allowed a goal. 
Susquehanna Valley swept Chenango Forks three sets to none on Thursday night in STAC volleyball action.
